<HEADLINE>
FT  28 APR 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A WEAKER financial rand boosted shares in companies with overseas income.
The overall index added 15 to 3,386, while the gold index rose 11 to 1,017.
Industrials put on 9 to 4,225. Anglos rose R1 to R111.75.
</TEXT>
