FT  27 APR 92 / World News in Brief: Earthquake
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An earthquake and two powerful aftershocks which jolted northern California
at the weekend caused damage estimated at Dollars 10m, destroyed scores of
homes and buildings, injured 70 people and left five missing.
