</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Increased pre-tax losses of IPounds 3.7m (Pounds 3.4m) were announced by
Youghal Carpets (Holdings), the County Cork-based carpets and textiles
group, for 1991. For 1990 the loss was IPounds 2.84m.
