FT  27 APR 92 / UK Company News: Acorn back to annual profit
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
ACORN COMPUTER Group covered from its first half loss to record a pre-tax
profit of Pounds 274,000 for 1991, compared to Pounds 1.58m.
The previous year included Pounds 561,000 exceptional credits.
Sales in the second half regained the levels of previous years to finish at
Pounds 40.9m (Pounds 45.5m), gross margins were improved and operating
expenses well controlled.
