bid from Lloyds.
To think of UK banks (and for that matter UK companies) in terms of being
non-European and to consider the effects of takeovers purely in terms of the
domestic market will not help British banks (or companies) to compete on an
equal footing with their French, German, Swiss and Spanish counterparts,
both in Europe and at a global level.
